---achievement_Dungeon Delver---
Kill :: [[Mobs/Caged Shocker|Caged Shocker]]@5 [[Mobs/Assassin|Assassin]]@5 [[Mobs/Bomb Bot|Bomb Bot]]@5 [[Mobs/Glitch Samurai|Glitch Samurai]]@2
Tags :: InDungeon
XP :: 50
Rewards :: [[27 Wyld Luck]]@1

Kill Caged Shockers, Assassins, Bomb Bots, and Glitch Samurais inside of dungeons.

Remember, you can always recall back to Haven if you get in too deep. Forget that at your own peril.

